The Roman Catholic Diocese of Cuenca (Latin: Conchen(sis)) is a diocese located in the city of Cuenca in the Ecclesiastical province of Toledo in Spain.[1][2]

History[edit]

  • July 5, 1183: Established as Diocese of Cuenca
